# 🧠 Resume Ranker AI

A simple and effective tool that ranks resumes based on how well they match a given job description — powered by Natural Language Processing and transformer embeddings.

## 🚀 Demo

Upload a job description, then upload multiple resume PDFs, and get an AI-generated similarity score for each resume.

## 📌 Features

- Extracts text from uploaded resume PDFs
- Converts resumes and job description into embeddings using `all-MiniLM-L6-v2`
- Calculates similarity using Cosine Similarity
- Ranks resumes from best to worst match
- Provides a download link for each uploaded resume

## 🛠️ Built With

- [Streamlit]
- [PyPDF2]
- [Sentence-Transformers]
- [Scikit-learn]